      <pattern name="R5 SC-18 bug evidence" location="projects/spaarke-ai-platform-unification-r5/notes/lessons-learned.md">
        Gap C — "Schema-aware rendering implicit (string-only widget)". The `tldr:
        string[]` rendered as raw JSON tokens; `entities` as raw JSON literal. The
        outputSchema document for this action MUST include these field types correctly
        typed so the widget can dispatch on them.
