  <context>
    <background>
      `summarize-document-for-workspace@v1` is the workspace-side summarization action.
      Its output renders in a workspace tab via `StructuredOutputStreamWidget`. R5 SC-18
      showed the widget rendering raw streaming JSON for non-string fields (`tldr` array,
      `entities` object) — Gap C in R5 lessons-learned. This task ships the data
      foundation for the fix: an explicit JSON Schema declaration of what the action
      produces, so the widget (tasks 040 + 041) can dispatch on field type.
    </background>
    <relevant-files>
      <file>scripts/Migrate-SumWorkspaceActionOutputSchema.ps1 (NEW)</file>
      <file>infra/dataverse/outputschemas/sum-workspace-v1.schema.json (NEW)</file>
      <file>projects/spaarke-ai-platform-unification-r6/notes/task-033-migration-evidence.md (NEW)</file>
    </relevant-files>
    <related-work>
      <item>Sibling tasks 032/034/035 migrate other actions in parallel (B-G2).</item>
      <item>Tasks 040 + 041 update `StructuredOutputStreamWidget` to read THIS action's outputSchema and render array/object fields correctly.</item>
      <item>R5 SC-18 walkthrough surfaced the rendering bugs this migration enables fixing.</item>
    </related-work>
  </context>

  <steps>
    <step order="0" name="Context Check + RIGOR LEVEL">
      Check context. Declare:

      ```
      🔒 RIGOR LEVEL: STANDARD
      📋 REASON: Data migration on production action; idempotency required; no code change
      📖 PROTOCOL STEPS: 8 steps; Step 9.5 quality gates SKIPPED per STANDARD rigor
      Proceeding with Step 0...
      ```
    </step>
    <step order="1" name="Review Progress">
      Read TASK-INDEX.md; confirm 033 status 🔲; deps (030, 031) complete.
    </step>
    <step order="2" name="Gather Resources">
      Read inputs + knowledge. Inspect the JPS source for SUM-WORKSPACE@v1 to find the
      EXACT output field list. Read R5 lessons-learned Gap C in full.
    </step>
    <step order="3" name="Author the JSON Schema Document">
      Create `infra/dataverse/outputschemas/sum-workspace-v1.schema.json`. Include:
      - `summary: string`
      - `tldr: array (items: string)`
      - `entities: object` with nested `organizations: array(string)` + `persons:
        array(string)`
      - Any other fields the JPS source declares.
      Validate against draft-07 meta-schema.
    </step>
    <step order="4" name="Author Migration Script">
      Create `scripts/Migrate-SumWorkspaceActionOutputSchema.ps1`:
      (a) GET action by alternate key `summarize-document-for-workspace@v1`;
      (b) Guard + PATCH `sprk_outputschemajson`;
      (c) GET playbook node referencing the action; PATCH `destination = workspace` and
          `widgetType = StructuredOutputStreamWidget` per task 031 storage surface;
      (d) Log all actions.
    </step>
    <step order="5" name="Apply to Spaarke Dev">
      Run script. Capture output + post-migration row state.
    </step>
    <step order="6" name="Verify Idempotency">
      Re-run; confirm no-op.
    </step>
    <step order="7" name="Regression Smoke Test">
      Trigger the workspace summarization path against a test document. Confirm: output
      renders to a workspace tab today (same as before; widget is not yet schema-aware).
      Record evidence.
    </step>
    <step order="8" name="Confirm Acceptance + Complete">
      Walk through acceptance criteria. Update TASK-INDEX.md: 033 🔲 → ✅. Reset
      `current-task.md`. Report completion. Note BFF publish-size delta = 0 MB.
    </step>
  </steps>

